After termination, You must stop using, distributing, hosting, and monetizing the Project Materials and VRAXION-Powered Functionality unless the Licensor agrees otherwise in writing.

Sections that by their nature should survive termination survive, including royalty obligations accrued before termination, audit rights, warranty disclaimers, liability limits, trademark restrictions, and governing law.

